annotationA: DNA polymerase delta small subunit; The function of the small subunit is not yet clear; Belongs to the DNA polymerase delta/II small subunit family
annotationB: Replication factor C subunit 2; The elongation of primed DNA templates by DNA polymerase delta and epsilon requires the action of the accessory proteins proliferating cell nuclear antigen (PCNA) and activator 1. Subunit 2 binds ATP
